Class ScriptConfigurationService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.scripting.service.ScriptConfigurationService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ServiceListener, ScriptingService

    public class ScriptConfigurationService
extends Object
implements ScriptingService, ServiceListener
    The ScriptConfigurationService for access to the persisted ScriptConfiguration instances. It is the layer on top of the ScriptConfigurationDataStore.
